  "description": "<p><strong>Mozilla本周公布了火狐OS操作系统“积极”升级策略：计划每三个月向合作伙伴发布新的版本升级，而且每一个半月发布一次安全更新。</strong>Mozilla发布管理经理亚历克斯•基博尔（Alex Keybl）声称“这样的开发进度是史无前例的”。很快，Firefox OS就将在8月中旬进行安全更新，然后在10月进行全面的系统更新。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2efedc82/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245573.htm&amp;t=Mozilla%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E8%88%AC%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E7%81%AB%E7%8B%90OS\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245573.htm&amp;t=Mozilla%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E8%88%AC%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E7%81%AB%E7%8B%90OS\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245573.htm&amp;t=Mozilla%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E8%88%AC%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E7%81%AB%E7%8B%90OS\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245573.htm&amp;t=Mozilla%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E8%88%AC%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E7%81%AB%E7%8B%90OS\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245573.htm&amp;t=Mozilla%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E8%